text: Hello everyone. I use `hfc` package for node.js, and when I call `Chain.enroll(…)` function I get error `Handshake failed with fatal error SSL_ERROR_SSL`. Can anybody help me to understand what goes wrong?

I use local network with `tls disabled`
actually I got rid of this error already. It was a typo. I set wrong protocol name to URL.
